description: Step on up to Van Eps Parks where you’ll find My Place Mobile Cafe, home to incredibly delicious home cooked meals. You’ll get served whatever they cookin’ up, and you’re sure to love it all. Biscuits & Gravy, Mac & Cheese, and Chicken & Stuffing Casserole are only just a few of the foods you may find on this rotating menu. For a taste of home away from home, you’re always invited to My Place Mobile Cafe where they’re cooking up something real special, just for you.
name: My Place Mobile Cafe
